Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
setTopCell(25.10)                                            setTopCell(25.10)

Name
       setTopCell  -  Switches  the  design  to the partition specified by the
       <cellName>

Syntax
       setTopCell <cellName>

       Switches the design to the partition specified by the <cellName>.

       Note: Cadence recommends that you use the same name for  the  top  cell
       and the partition.

       You can use this command only after you commit the partition.

Parameters
       <cellName>
              The name of the top cell that indicates a different partition.

              Data_type: string, required

Related Information
              * Hierarchical  Flow  Capabilities  chapter  in the Innovus User
                Guide

                * Partitioning the Design - Restoring the Top-Level  Floorplan
                  with Partition Data

